When was Raymond Felton drafted?

Raymond Felton was drafted by Charlotte Bobcats, 1st round (5th pick, 5th overall), 2005 NBA Draft.

What position did Raymond Felton play?

Point Guard and Shooting Guard.

When did Raymond Felton retire?

Raymond Felton last played in 2019.

What is Raymond Felton's net worth?

Raymond Felton made at least $54,171,012 playing professional basketball.

How much did Raymond Felton make?

Raymond Felton made $7,560,000 in 2012.

What did Raymond Felton average?

Raymond Felton averaged 11.2 points, 3.0 rebounds, and 5.2 assists per game.

How many rings does Raymond Felton have?

Raymond Felton won 0 championships.

What schools did Raymond Felton attend?

Raymond Felton attended Latta in Latta, South Carolina and UNC.

What are Raymond Felton's nicknames?

Felts is a nickname for Raymond Felton.
